---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="Cyber Security Services | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="Comprehensive cyber security services including penetration testing, vulnerability assessment, network security, and compliance in the UAE."
  path="/services/cyber-security/"
>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <img width="48" src="/img/logo.webp" alt="GeneralSoft Logo"/>
        <span class="logo-text">Generalsoft<span class="logo-legal">FZ-LLC</span></span>
      </a>
      <span class="lang-switch"><a href="/ar/services/cyber-security/">العربية</a></span>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li class="dropdown">
          <a href="#services" class="dropbtn">Services <span class="dropdown-arrow">▼</span></a>
          <div class="dropdown-content">
            <a href="/services/custom-software/">Custom Software Development</a>
            <a href="/services/education-training/">Education & Training</a>
            <a href="/services/ai-development/">AI Development</a>
            <a href="/services/systems-design/">Systems & Software Design</a>
            <a href="/services/cyber-security/">Cyber Security</a>
            <a href="/services/web-design/">Web & Network Design</a>
            <a href="/services/mobile-apps/">Mobile Applications</a>
            <a href="/services/electronic-systems/">Electronic Systems</a>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li><a href="/contact/">Contact Us</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#about">About Us</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="service-content" id="security-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2>Comprehensive Cyber Security Services</h2>
      <p>In today's digital landscape, security is not optional — it's essential. We deliver enterprise-grade security solutions that protect your infrastructure, applications, and data from evolving cyber threats.</p>

      <h3>Security Assessment & Auditing</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Vulnerability Assessment</h4><p>Comprehensive scanning and analysis of your systems to identify security weaknesses before attackers can exploit them.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Penetration Testing</h4><p>Ethical hacking services that simulate real-world attacks to test your defenses and identify critical vulnerabilities.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Security Auditing</h4><p>Detailed evaluation of your security policies, procedures, and controls to ensure compliance and best practices.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Risk Assessment</h4><p>Identify, analyze, and prioritize security risks to make informed decisions about resource allocation and mitigation strategies.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>Application Security</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Secure Code Review — Static and dynamic analysis to identify security flaws in source code</li>
        <li>Web Application Security Testing — OWASP Top 10 vulnerability testing and remediation</li>
        <li>API Security — Protecting APIs from unauthorized access and data breaches</li>
        <li>Mobile App Security — Comprehensive security testing for iOS and Android applications</li>
        <li>DevSecOps Integration — Embedding security into CI/CD pipeline for continuous protection</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Network & Infrastructure Security</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Firewall Management</h4><p>Design, implement, and manage next-generation firewalls to control network traffic and block threats.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Intrusion Detection & Prevention</h4><p>Real-time monitoring and automated response to suspicious network activity and potential breaches.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>VPN & Secure Access</h4><p>Implement secure remote access solutions with multi-factor authentication and encryption.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>DDoS Protection</h4><p>Defend against distributed denial-of-service attacks that can disrupt your services.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>Data Protection & Encryption</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Data Encryption</h4><p>Protect sensitive data at rest and in transit with industry-standard encryption protocols.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Data Loss Prevention</h4><p>Monitor and control data movement to prevent unauthorized data exfiltration.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Backup & Disaster Recovery</h4><p>Secure backup solutions with disaster recovery planning for business continuity.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Database Security</h4><p>Protect your databases from SQL injection, unauthorized access, and data breaches.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>Compliance & Governance</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>GDPR Compliance:</strong> Implement controls to protect EU citizen data and ensure privacy compliance</li>
        <li><strong>ISO 27001:</strong> Implement ISMS and support certification</li>
        <li><strong>PCI DSS:</strong> Payment card industry compliance for organizations handling card transactions</li>
        <li><strong>SOC 2:</strong> Security, availability, and confidentiality controls for service organizations</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Our Security Framework</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>NIST Cybersecurity Framework:</strong> Identify, Protect, Detect, Respond, Recover</li>
        <li><strong>CIS Controls:</strong> Prioritized set of actions to protect organizations from cyber attacks</li>
        <li><strong>OWASP Guidelines:</strong> Security best practices for web and mobile applications</li>
        <li><strong>Zero Trust Architecture:</strong> "Never trust, always verify" approach to network security</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container"><div class="contact-content">
      <h2>Secure Your Digital Future Today</h2>
      <p>Don't wait for a breach to take security seriously. Contact our security experts for a comprehensive assessment.</p>
      <div class="contact-info">
        <div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-item-icon">🌐</div><strong>Website</strong><a href="https://generalsoft.ae">generalsoft.ae</a></div>
        <div class="contact-item"><a href="/contact/"><div class="contact-item-icon">📧</div><strong>Contact Us</strong><br>Get in touch</a></div>
        <div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-item-icon">📍</div><strong>Location</strong><span>Ras Al Khaimah</span></div>
      </div>
    </div></div>
  </section>

</Layout>
